		</head>
	<body>
		<outline text="June 2021" type="calendarMonth" name="june2021" >
			<outline text="June 15" type="calendarDay" name="15" >
				<outline text="With the newly added plugins API, the sky is the limit when it comes to extending Logseq's abilities. For users, post your plugin feature request here: https://t.co/mRd66ZxRYh; For those who'd like to develop a plugin, ask anything here: https://t.co/t6PyoUcndE." type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 02:53:04 GMT" tweetId="1404995412587532294" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404995412587532294" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="With the newly added plugins API, the sky is the limit when it comes to extending Logseq's abilities. For users, post your plugin feature request here: https://t.co/mRd66ZxRYh; For those who'd like to develope a plugin, ask anything here: https://t.co/t6PyoUcndE." type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 02:51:12 GMT" tweetId="1404994941084868608" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404994941084868608" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Thank you! And congrats to our first [[Logseq Hobbit]] @pengx17! [[Logseq Hobbits]] are those core contributors who're making Logseq better and who'd like to explore different ways for better thoughts! https://t.co/01LuXgR8qQ" type="tweet" created="Tue, 15 Jun 2021 16:46:18 GMT" tweetId="1404842712549904389" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404842712549904389" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Also, thrilled to announce that our draft Plugins API is out! 🚀🚀 The documentation is at https://t.co/IBttXXklLx
We have a [[Plugins 101]] page too, https://t.co/N5sI38L3ta

Any feedback or suggestions are appreciated!" type="tweet" created="Tue, 15 Jun 2021 16:09:51 GMT" tweetId="1404833539959312385" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404833539959312385" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="0.1.8 is just out, OPML import is supported now! https://t.co/quSY3ydkRi" type="tweet" created="Tue, 15 Jun 2021 16:05:04 GMT" tweetId="1404832337595039751" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404832337595039751" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Guess what? We have a live `calc` mode now! @sebasbensu Thank you so much for making this happen! 🎉🎉 #opensource https://t.co/ROrkdCCQFm" type="tweet" created="Tue, 15 Jun 2021 15:59:42 GMT" tweetId="1404830986873962501" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404830986873962501" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 14" type="calendarDay" name="14" >
				<outline text="Awesome! https://t.co/7j86iCjQTz" type="tweet" created="Mon, 14 Jun 2021 12:46:16 GMT" tweetId="1404419921535279105" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404419921535279105" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Yes! You can use Obsidian's mobile app to open the Logseq folder. You can also use any other mobile apps that support Markdown or Org mode. https://t.co/tfvqmwN6OV" type="tweet" created="Mon, 14 Jun 2021 12:44:05 GMT" tweetId="1404419370986577920" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404419370986577920" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Thank you for the shout out! https://t.co/fLp7D7cMDe" type="tweet" created="Mon, 14 Jun 2021 12:40:39 GMT" tweetId="1404418508708974605" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404418508708974605" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Beautiful! We have a publish prototype which is using the JSON export, your devlog looks better! https://t.co/AuKFcsH5qJ" type="tweet" created="Mon, 14 Jun 2021 12:39:28 GMT" tweetId="1404418210263232512" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404418210263232512" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 12" type="calendarDay" name="12" >
				<outline text="Big fan of OPML, the OPML import is coming soon. https://t.co/67F4PwsbFm" type="tweet" created="Sun, 13 Jun 2021 01:46:39 GMT" tweetId="1403891532617293825" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1403891532617293825" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="@djwhitt thank you for your donation 🙏 - Your contribution means a lot to us!
https://t.co/KGsf0HWKvQ" type="tweet" created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 20:03:17 GMT" tweetId="1403805121570611200" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1403805121570611200" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="0.1.7 is just out! Full changelog at https://t.co/4f6qjMwkBh https://t.co/cz7n2HqS7e" type="tweet" created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 12:52:07 GMT" tweetId="1403696615567753218" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1403696615567753218" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Thank you for the good words! We're actually looking for some funds to make Logseq better, if anyone is interested in or has recommendations, both DM and replies are welcome, RTs appreciated 🙏 https://t.co/9BW8hOvOIJ" type="tweet" created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 07:57:58 GMT" tweetId="1403622590283800581" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1403622590283800581" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Interesting! https://t.co/lYvAmkd3kI" type="tweet" created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 07:19:20 GMT" tweetId="1403612867090284547" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1403612867090284547" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				</outline>
			</outline>
		</body>
